&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Total OneinStack Install Time: &lt;span class="m">28&lt;/span> minutes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
